|consulté le= 14 novembre 2009}}.</ref>{{,}}<ref>{{article |langue=en
|url= http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/finance/2009/1113/1224258721485.html
|titre= Secret agreement may have poisonous effect on the net
|nom= Danny O'Brien
|périodique= [[The Irish Times]]
|jour= 13 |mois= novembre |année= 2009
|consulté le= 14 novembre 2009}}</ref>{{,}}<ref>{{article |langue=en
|url= http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/g/a/2009/11/11/apop111109.DTL&tsp=1
